::Kaiser::
       He looks up from his station.  "There is a veritable conflagration on 
here."  He points to a portion of the map as it flashes.  "It appears that 
there are Maximals, Predacons, and Tripreds fighting against other Predacons. 
 Very strange."  He returns to his scanning of the planet.  "There are other 
bots there of sources that I do not recognize.  But they all seem to be 
concentrated there.
